        "title": "6. `fetchers.py` — the largest gap. Untested: retry/backoff logic, every `parse_*` normalizer, every pagination loop, and the Meta/Google scraping edge cases.",
        "content": "\nThis module is explicitly designed to be unit-testable via an injectable client (per its own docstring) — that intent is entirely unrealized right now.\n\n",
